. * =========================================================
. * FACTORS AFFECTING OUTPUT OF FIRMS IN VIETNAM'S FURNITURE INDUSTRY
. * Panel Data Analysis, 2012-2018  |  VSIC 31
. * =========================================================

. use furniture_panel, clear
. xtset firm_id year

       panel variable:  firm_id (unbalanced)
        time variable:  year, 2012 to 2018
                delta:  1 unit

. * -------------------------------------------------------
. * MODEL 1: Pooled OLS (baseline)
. * -------------------------------------------------------

. reg lnOutput lnLabor lnCapital Leverage lnWage lnSize, robust

